So you guys probably all
had different stories,

00:24:35.610 --> 00:24:37.970
we just wanted to see, what
are some commonalities that

00:24:37.970 --> 00:24:40.187
came about from your tables?

00:24:40.187 --> 00:24:42.020
So anyone willing to
share out what you guys

00:24:42.020 --> 00:24:43.730
noticed about your failures?

00:24:43.730 --> 00:24:45.650
Any, kind of, aha moments?

00:24:45.650 --> 00:24:48.710
Any common failures
that you tend to have?

00:24:48.710 --> 00:24:50.370
Common support that you need?

00:24:50.370 --> 00:24:51.690
Any of that sort.

